<br>
We get the three pieces again, come back the next day (had to be 14hrs) he hands in staff first to start the MQ and completes the quest.<br>
<br>
Although we correctly MQed the sky turn in and I got my epic I think this points out that NPCs hold items indefinitely till they despawn or are killed.<br>
